SIEM = Security Information & Event Management

Collects logs from multiple sources â†’ correlates â†’ detects threats.

Core functions:

Log Collection (Windows, Linux, Firewalls, IDS/IPS).

Normalization (convert into readable format).

Correlation (detect suspicious patterns).

Alerting & Dashboarding.

Incident Investigation.

ðŸ”¹ 2. Popular SIEM Tools

